By using Emoji Creator, you agree to the collection and use of information as outlined below.

---

## 1. Information We Collect

We collect limited information necessary to provide and improve the app‚Äôs features.

### a. User-Generated Content

* The emojis, stickers, or images you create or import are stored **locally on your device**.
* If you choose to back up, share, or sync your creations, they may also be **securely uploaded to our server**.
* We do not access or share your files without your consent.

### b. Device and Usage Information

We may collect anonymous technical data such as:

* Device model and operating system version
* App version, crash logs, and usage statistics
* Non-personal identifiers like **Advertising ID** (for ads personalization)

This helps us improve app performance and compatibility.

### c. Advertising Data

We use **Google AdMob** and similar services to display ads. These networks may collect:

* Advertising ID
* Approximate location (for ad relevance)
* App usage and interaction data

You can opt out of personalized ads anytime in your device‚Äôs ad settings.

---

## 2. Permissions We Use and Why

Our app requests the following Android permissions only to enable core functionality:

| Permission                                                                                                              | Purpose                                                                                                                           |
| ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `INTERNET`                                                                                                              | To show ads, connect to servers for emoji backup, and update content.                                                             |
| `READ_MEDIA_IMAGES`, `READ_MEDIA_VIDEO`, `READ_MEDIA_AUDIO`, `READ_MEDIA_VISUAL_USER_SELECTED`, `READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE` | To allow you to import or use your own photos, videos, or media in emoji creation. Access is limited to user-selected files only. |
| `WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE`                                                                                                | To save emoji creations to your device gallery (used only on older Android versions).                                             |
| `ACCESS_MEDIA_LOCATION`                                                                                                 | To access location metadata embedded in selected media files (EXIF data) ‚Äî only if you choose to import such media.               |
| `VIBRATE`                                                                                                               | To provide optional haptic feedback during emoji editing or saving.                                                               |

We never access, collect, or share files without user action or permission.

---

## 3. How We Use the Information

We use the collected data to:

* Enable emoji creation, saving, and sharing features.
* Provide app functionality and cloud backup.
* Display relevant ads to keep the app free.
* Improve performance and troubleshoot issues.
* Maintain app security and prevent abuse.

We **do not sell, rent, or trade** your personal data.

---

## 4. Data Storage and Retention

* **Local data:** Your emoji creations remain stored on your device and can be deleted anytime through the app or by uninstalling it.
* **Server data:** If you choose to save creations online, they are stored securely on our cloud servers and deleted upon your request or account deletion.
* We retain data only as long as needed for app functionality.

---

## 5. Sharing Your Information

We only share limited information in the following cases:

* **With service providers:** e.g., AdMob, Firebase, or cloud storage providers to enable ads and backup features.
* **When required by law:** If we must respond to lawful requests by authorities.

All partners comply with applicable data protection regulations.

Third-party privacy policies:

* [Google AdMob Privacy & Terms](https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads)
* [Firebase Privacy Policy](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)

---

## 6. Your Privacy Rights

Depending on your region, you may have the right to:

* Access or delete your stored data.
* Opt out of personalized advertising.
* Withdraw consent to data collection.

To exercise these rights, contact us at **[your contact email]**.
You can also delete all locally stored data by uninstalling the app.

---

## 7. Data Security

We use industry-standard measures to protect stored data, including encryption in transit and access control.
While we strive for maximum protection, no system is 100% secure, so we encourage users to use caution when sharing media.

---

## 8. Children‚Äôs Privacy

Emoji Creator is intended for general audiences and is **not directed toward children under 13** (or under 16 in the EU).
We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors.
If a parent or guardian believes that their child has provided personal data, they can contact us to request deletion.

